{
  "stem": "2533.2",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just behind the big gates, or take him away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The slightest thing that he didn't like that person did, he wasn't living anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, that [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wagner. ?] We haven't got any words how-- how he-- how he was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the 23rd of September, '42, a transport of ration POWs were brought in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were still in there from [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Kharkov, ?] maybe another city in Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were still in their military uniforms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] And amongst them was a lieutenant with the name of Alexander Pechersky.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think my-- no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could maybe write it down for you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it's all in the books.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was so known.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we used to call him Sasha.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was stationed there, you know, with all the other workers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were working a lot of other places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was-- he heard what was going on in that camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day he heard a little girl screaming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had at home in Russia a three-years-old daughter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the people-- the boys in the camp before that transport arrived, we were already planning an escape because a lot of them wanted.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Single escapes were never good because they used to caught them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And besides that, they always used to have-- 10 or 20 more used to be executed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But before that-- I just-- you know, before that-- that was in-- in the summer, June or July.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a [INAUDIBLE] kommando.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were working outside in the forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were going to fetch water, and they didn't come back-- two of them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were caught, and the whole [INAUDIBLE] kommando was brought to-- they used to call it sportplatz.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
